cosmic-applet-bongo-penguin (0.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial public release.
    - COSMIC applet: works in both panel and dock.
    - System-wide keyboard & mouse capture via evdev (one tokio task per
      device, epoll-backed — no polling, no battery drain).
    - Live keystroke counter with AES-256-GCM encrypted persistence
      bound to /etc/machine-id; atomic writes safe against the two
      parallel dock instances COSMIC spawns per output.
    - Four-pose SVG animation: idle / left flipper / right flipper /
      both flippers, with 120 ms decay back to idle.
    - Popup with Cosmetics / Achievements / About tabs.

 -- YockerFX Mon, 20 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000
